  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FRANTIC PARTY FUN FOR FRIENDS & FAMILY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chompy Chomp Chomp Party</strong> is a chaotic 1–8 player party game built for laughter, shouting, and couch-multiplayer chaos. Chase, chomp, and outplay your friends and family in fast, silly matches that anyone can pick up and enjoy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/26c80ac14be9350eccacda08f16c16f6.poster.avif?t=1766162731\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/26c80ac14be9350eccacda08f16c16f6.webm?t=1766162731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/26c80ac14be9350eccacda08f16c16f6.mp4?t=1766162731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WHY YOU'LL LOVE IT</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perfect for families & mixed ages:</strong> Simple controls, instant fun</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Plays up to 8 players locally:</strong> Ideal for parties and game nights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Short, replayable matches:</strong> Jump in, laugh, play again</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Loads of variety:</strong> Multiple modes, levels and surprises</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy to learn, hard to master:</strong> Fun immediately, depth over time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're playing with friends, kids, or a mix of both, Chompy Chomp Chomp Party keeps everyone involved.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TOURNAMENT MODE: TURN CHAOS INTO COMPETITION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Set up tournaments with custom modes and levels, battle for trophies, and settle scores with Sudden Death tie-breakers. From friendly family rivalries to full-on competitive chaos, tournaments turn every session into an event.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/77a05b4593baed69d4674cdf01508d28.poster.avif?t=1766162731\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/77a05b4593baed69d4674cdf01508d28.webm?t=1766162731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/77a05b4593baed69d4674cdf01508d28.mp4?t=1766162731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >POWER-UPS & MAYHEM</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With colourful visuals, catchy music, and endlessly replayable gameplay, <strong>Chompy Chomp Chomp Party</strong> is ideal for cosy winter evenings, holiday gatherings, and anytime you want something fun to play together.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’ve got five minutes or a whole evening, it’s easy to jump in... and hard to stop playing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/359b72ea4ba250d1be00d88d7d1ea332.poster.avif?t=1766162731\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/359b72ea4ba250d1be00d88d7d1ea332.webm?t=1766162731\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479850/extras/359b72ea4ba250d1be00d88d7d1ea332.mp4?t=1766162731\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >See a list of accessibility features on The Family Video Game Database: </p>",
